PORTLAND, Ore. -- It's Week 7 of the high school football season as we enter the final third of the season. With that, there is no shortage of great games. 
KGW's Game of the Week 
KGW's Game of the Week is Jefferson at Benson JV football game. 
We'll have full highlights from the game on Friday Night Flights! KGW sports anchor Joe Becker is at the game for his Bite of the Night. Chunky, McKinzie & Jake from 98.7 The Bull will also be at the game.
